snippet.title: Tetra Cube Game PV [EN]
snippet.description:
Available on Steam  :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1520680

Tetra Cube is a turn-based strategy roguelike game.
Nae and Dio are dispatched to information that an unknown Cube caused a disaster. Whether you can't beat the Cube is up to you.

Creator : https://twitter.com/ddal_kr
